# RTEC Report layout (SETUP Form 002)

## Scope

- **Print only** — on-screen preview in `RtecReportPreview.tsx` stays modern/summary layout.
- Official output via `RtecReportDocument` rendered at print time (`printRtecReportPdf`).

## Document title

`SETUP Form 002 · RTEC Report`

## Pagination

- Physical page footers via named `@page rtec-report-sheet` with `counter(page)` / `counter(pages)` in `@bottom-center`.
- No per-section inline footers (avoid cross-bleed with TNA / Project Proposal forms).
- `FormBlock` + `break-inside: avoid` — section titles stay with content; long tables may break across pages.

## Print path

- In-page `window.print()` via `#rtec-report-print-root` + `body.rtec-report-printing`.
- `createRoot` render (do not clone preview; do not use popup `document.write`).
- Hide portal metadata in print: no Application ID from preview.

## Official sections (order)

Cover + cost split → I. Brief description (company profile with checkbox grids, objectives, expected outputs) → II. Compliance → III. Highlights (management, technical, marketing, financial, waste, risk) → IV. Recommendation + signatures.

## Shared checkbox grids

Company profile reuses `PP_ORGANIZATION_TYPES`, `PP_PROFIT_TYPES`, `PP_MSME_SIZES`, `PP_BUSINESS_ACTIVITY_PAIRS` from project proposal layout via `isOptionChecked()`. Registration offices include **LGU** (`RTEC_REGISTRATION_OFFICES`).

## Attachments (print slots)

- `orgChart` — III.a Management
- `plantLayout` — III.b Technical constraints section

